(Republished)

In the Matter of Walter D., Jr., et al. New York Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Children, Respondent; Walter D., Sr., Appellant.

Order, Family Court, New York County, entered on May 7, 1979, unanimously affirmed, without costs and without disbursements. The order of this court entered on October 9, 1980 [78 AD2d 784] is vacated. No opinion. Concur — Kupferman, J. P., Birns, Fein, Sandler and Carro, JJ.
